		<description><![CDATA[Very very informative Scott. As I’m becoming busier by the day with remote session recordings and it helps to see someone laying down the ground rules for you as opposed to having to figure everything out by yourself.

I just wonder how many producers provide you with a chord chart or at least a road map for the song structure? By far I was able to convince most of the producers I’ve worked with to send me a chord chart along with every project. To me it is super essential.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Very very informative Scott. As I’m becoming busier by the day with remote session recordings and it helps to see someone laying down the ground rules for you as opposed to having to figure everything out by yourself.</p>
<p>I just wonder how many producers provide you with a chord chart or at least a road map for the song structure? By far I was able to convince most of the producers I’ve worked with to send me a chord chart along with every project. To me it is super essential.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
